{"tid":118742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"渣馬52歲女跑手延至下午不治","createTime":"2017-02-13T08:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T12:51:16.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24fa0e38587af73c58d13b46a969b9215953ad66","tid":118742,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"參加香港馬拉松賽事昏迷受傷危殆的52歲女跑手，在東區醫院深切治療部留醫，延至下午三時四十一分死亡。另外亦有六名傷者留院，情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n該名52歲女跑手，於維園終點前暈倒，在丈夫陪同下送往律敦治醫院，其間需用自動心肺復甦機救援，其後再轉送東區醫院深切治療部留醫。大會指，該女跑手是首次參賽，深切治療部報告指她心臟有問題。"},{"pid":"7770c134ce19b2252596f2e91cd530ea321ca96a","tid":118742,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"搏盡無悔.jpg呢"},{"pid":"0799eb69ca66b689ca1d1da4a8445e3b3a9ff1f0","tid":118742,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8405ea148faba6296ea311474eed8f69400185fb","tid":118742,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/164218_b1a66b427bdac872748a3a80cf399a65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F164218_b1a66b427bdac872748a3a80cf399a65.jpg&h=e8a602fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61a8b1c92e35b4e633d39eb8e20a859d984438ef","tid":118742,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"fe9085116cabace9b063aa04566da0f560cfa8e9","tid":118742,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80e73a3398b4a54c08a29f34401d1a2225dec761","tid":118742,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"下年大家報名之後, 要諗下自己係咪可以為左跑10km無左條命之後無後悔"},{"pid":"d27d9b38d557da7130193079cba594141e747a98","tid":118742,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0